Summary: This report was filed by Dispatch on behalf of witness.
divs: Sighting DetailsThis report was filed by Dispatch on behalf of witness. Witness reported seeing an illuminated, large, cylindrical object at a distance of about 10-20 miles away. He estimated the object's size as three times that of a commercial airliner, and said it looked like a 737 with no wings. After watching for several minutes, the object disappeared from view as he was watching it. This witness has a history of UFO events going back several decades, and also mentioned incidents of finding what he believes may have been implants on his body, which eventually disappeared.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Centrahoma
